data.description: They don't get anymore move-in ready than this! This immaculate 3 BR, 2 1/2 BA home is located in desirable Mt View & is ready for new owners. You can see the pride in home ownership the minute you enter the front door. Some of the recent updates include: kitchen remodel with custom cabinets & counter tops, remodeled bathrooms, crown molding, new light fixtures thru-out...and that's just updates completed this year! New windows in 2017 & waterproof plank flooring complement the bright, fresh feeling of this beautiful home. Lots of possibilities for the finished basement, which has plenty of room for the family to just hang out or can be converted into the perfect man cave. Basement features stained concrete floors, a wood burning fireplace, a half bath & a pool table which owners are leaving with the home. Nice deck overlooking the backyard. Recently purchased 10 x 16 storage shed to remain with the home as well.  Don't miss your opportunity to see this home!
